Good Evening Bill,
Recently, we started a company called The Bioinformatics Network, an=20=20
efficient=20and adaptive company that can cater to the needs of=20=20
professors/researchers=20that require next-generation sequencing data=20=20
processing=20services. After obtaining bioinformatics training=20=20
throughout=20my Ph.D. and post-doctoral fellowship, I realized my future=20=
