platforms.=20This experience also made me realize the need for=20=20
streamlining=20this data processing step in genetics research to=20=20
increase=20the rate at which this data can be available for analysis.=C2=A0
=C2=A0
We understand that research projects can be stalled for months and=20=20
even=20years due to unavailable bioinformatics expertise and personnel=20=
