because=20poorly developed analyses can result in false conclusions that=20=
=20
may=20affect not only publications but the subsequent allocation of=20=20
money=20and efforts. The Bioinformatics Network provides customizable=20=20
bioinformatics=20pipelines that meet the specific criteria required for=20=
